  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <lg xml:id="TolC250">
          <l>avaitām,</l>
          <l>puṇariya ṉilaiyiṭaip poruṇilaik kutanavum</l>
          <l>viṉaiceyaṉ maruṅkiṟ kālamoṭu varunavum</l>
          <l>vēṟṟumaip poruḷvayi ṉurupā kunavu</l>
          <l>macainilaik kiḷavi yāki varunavu</l>
          <l>micainiṟaik kiḷavi yāki varunavun</l>
          <l>tattaṅ kuṟippiṟ poruḷcey kunavu</l>
          <l>moppil vaḻiyāṟ poruḷcey kunavumeṉ</l>
          <l>ṟappaṇ piṉavē nuvaluṅ kālai.</l>
        </lg>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <head>Iḷampūraṇar</head>
        <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Namaccivāya Mutaliyār</persName> 1931, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZMelJhy.TVA_BOK_0007521/page/157/mode/1up">157</ref>.</p>
      <p xml:id="TolC250-Ilam1">
varalāṟu: puṇariyal nilaiyiṭaip poruḷnilaik kutavuvaṉa: ‘iṉṉē vaṟṟē’ [eḻuttu. puṇari - 17] eṉṉun toṭakkattaṉa.
          </p>
      <p xml:id="TolC250-Ilam2">
viṉaiceyal maruṅkil kālamoṭu varuvaṉa: ‘aṉ āṉ’ ― ‘am ām’ ― [col. viṉaiyi - 8, 5] eṉṉun toṭakkattaṉa.
          </p>
      <p xml:id="TolC250-Ilam3">
vēṟṟumaip poruḷvayiṉ urupāvaṉa: ‘ai, oṭu, ku, iṉ, atu, kaṇ, viḷi’ [col. vēṟṟumai - 3] eṉṉun toṭakkattaṉa.
          </p>
      <p xml:id="TolC250-Ilam4">
acainilaik kiḷavi:
          </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC250-Ilam4-q1">
            <l>‘kēṇmiyā’,</l>
          </lg>
      <lg xml:id="TolC250-Ilam4-q2">
            <l>‘kaṇṭikum’</l>
          </lg>
      <p xml:id="TolC250-Ilam5">
[<ref target="../Purananuru/PN251.xml?highlight=[id%3D'PN251'] .l%3Anth-of-type(3)">puṟam - 251</ref>] eṉṉun toṭakkattaṉa.
          </p>
      <p xml:id="TolC250-Ilam6">
maṟṟaiyaṉa muṉṉē virikkiṉṟār. (2)
          </p>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <head>Cēṉāvaraiyar</head>
        <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Ci. Vai. Tamōtarampiḷḷai</persName> 1868, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/tolkppiyamcollat00unse/page/n206/mode/1up">203</ref>–<ref target="https://archive.org/details/tolkppiyamcollat00unse/page/n208/mode/1up">205</ref>.</p>
      <p xml:id="TolC250-Cena1">
i - ḷ. mēṟcollappaṭṭa iṭaiccoṟkaṭām, iraṇṭucoṟpuṇarumiṭattu apporuṇilaikkutavuvaṉavum, viṉaiccollai muṭikkumiṭattuk kālapporuḷavāy varuvaṉavum, ceyappaṭuporuṇmutalākiya vēṟṟumaipporuṭkaṇ urupeṉṉuṅkuṟiyavāy varuvaṉavum, poruḷuṭaiya vaṉṟic cārttic collappaṭuntuṇaiyāy varuvaṉavum, vēṟuporuḷuṇarttātu icainiṟaittalē poruḷāka varuvaṉavum, tattaṅkuṟippāṟporuḷuṇarttuvaṉavum, oppumai tōṉṟutavaḻi avvoppumaipporuḷ payappaṉavumeṉak kūṟappaṭṭa ēḻiyalpaiyuṭaiya collumiṭattu. e-ṟu.
          </p>
      <p xml:id="TolC250-Cena2">
puṇariyaṉilai puṇariyalatu nilai. āṇṭup poruṇilaik kutavutalāvatu, ellāvaṟṟaiyum eṉpuḻi vaṟṟuccāriyai nilaimoḻipporuḷ aḵṟiṇaipporuḷeṉpatu paṭa varutalum, ellānammaiyum eṉpuḻi nammuccāriyai apporuḷ taṉmaippaṉmaiyeṉpatu paṭa varutalumām. allaṉavum tāñ cārntu varum moḻipporuṭku upakāramuṭaiyavāy varumāṟōrntukoḷḷappaṭum. allākkāl, cāriyai moḻiyākāveṉpatu.
          </p>
      <p xml:id="TolC250-Cena3">
viṉaiccol orucollāyiṉum mutaṉilaiyum iṟutinilaiyum iṭaiccollumākap pirittuc ceykai ceytu kāṭṭappaṭutaliṉ, viṉaiceyaṉmaruṅkiṉeṉṟār. ammuṭipuṇarttāmaikkuk kāraṇam “puṇariya ṉilaiyiṭai yuṇarat tōṉṟā” eṉpuḻic collappaṭṭatu. avaṟṟuḷ orucāraṉa pāluṇarttāmaiyāṉum, ellāṅ kālamuṇarttutalāṉum, kālamoṭu varunavumeṉṟār.
          </p>
      <p xml:id="TolC250-Cena4">
vēṟṟumaipporuḷavāy varuvaṉa piṟacollumuḷavākaliṉ, avaṟṟai nīkkutaṟku urupākunavumeṉṟār. piṟacollāvaṉa 
          </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC250-Cena4-q1">
          <l>‘kaṇṇakaṉ ñālam,’<app><note xml:lang="en">Cf. <title xml:lang="ta">Puṟanāṉūṟu</title> 35.</note></app></l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:id="TolC250-Cena4-q2">
          <l>‘ūrkkā ṉivanta potumpar’<app><note xml:lang="en">Cf. <title xml:lang="ta">Kalittokai</title> 56, <ref target="../Kalittokai/Kali056.xml?highlight=%5Bid%3D%22Kali56%22%5D%20.l%3Anth-of-type(1)">line 1</ref>.</note></app></l>
        </lg>
      <p xml:id="TolC250-Cena5">
eṉa ēḻāmvēṟṟumaipporuṭkaṇ varuṅ kaṇ kāl mutalāyiṉavum,
        </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC250-Cena5-q1">
          <l>‘aṉaiyai yākaṉ māṟē;’<app><note xml:lang="en">Cf. <title xml:lang="ta">Puṟanāṉūṟu</title> 4.</note></app></l>
        </lg>
      <lg xml:id="TolC250-Cena5-q2">
          <l>‘ciṟantōṉ peyaraṉ piṟanta māṟē;’<app><note xml:lang="en">Cf. <title xml:lang="ta">Naṟṟiṇai</title> 40, <ref target="../Narrinai/NA40.xml?highlight=%5Bid%3D%22NA40%22%5D%20.l%3Anth-of-type(12)">line 12</ref>.</note></app></l>
        </lg>
      <lg xml:id="TolC250-Cena5-q3">
          <l>‘iyalpuḷi kōlōccu maṉṉavaṉ’<app><note xml:lang="en">Cf. <title xml:lang="ta">Tirukkuṟaḷ</title> 545, <ref target="../Tirukkural/TK545.xml?highlight=%5Bid%3D%22TK545%22%5D%20.l%3Anth-of-type(1)">line 1</ref>.</note></app></l>
        </lg>
      <p xml:id="TolC250-Cena6">
eṉa mūṉṟāmvēṟṟumaipporuṭkaṇ varum māṟu uḷi eṉpaṉavum, aṉṉa piṟavumām. aḵtēl, vēṟṟumaiyurupumeṉṟōtuvār; ōtavē, ivai nīṅkumeṉiṉ;―aḵtokkum. avaitammaiyuntaḻīikkōṭaṟku vēṟṟumaipporuḷvayiṉeṉṟār. avai varuṅkāl nilaimoḻiyurupiṟkēṟṟa ceykai ēṟpuḻip peṟutalumuṭaimaiyiṉ, urupākunavumeṉṟār. iḵtiruporuḷuṇarttalāṉ irutoṭarākak koḷka.
        </p>
      <p xml:id="TolC250-Cena7">
acaittal cārttutal. poruḷuṇarttātu peyaroṭum viṉaiyoṭuñ cārttic collappaṭṭu niṟṟaliṉ, acainilaiyāyiṟṟu. avai antiṉmutalāyiṉ.
          </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC250-Cena7-q1">
          <l>‘pukaḻntiku mallarō peritē;’</l>
        </lg>
      <lg xml:id="TolC250-Cena7-q2">
          <l>‘uraitticiṉōrē’</l>
        </lg>
      <p xml:id="TolC250-Cena8">
eṉac cārnta moḻiyai vēṟupaṭuttu niṟṟaliṉ, acainilaic collāyiṉaveṉpārumuḷar.
          </p>
      <p xml:id="TolC250-Cena9">
ceyyuṭkaṇ icai niṟaittu niṟṟaliṉ, icainiṟaiyāyiṉ.
          </p>
      <p xml:id="TolC250-Cena10">
kuṟippuc colluvāṉkaṇṇatāyiṉum avaṉ kuṟittaporuḷait tāṅkuṟittu niṟṟaliṉ, tattaṅkuṟippiṉeṉṟār. colluvāṉ kuṟitta poruḷait tām viḷakkumeṉavē,
          </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC250-Cena10-q1">
          <l>‘kūriyatōrvāḷ’</l>
        </lg>
      <p xml:id="TolcC250-Cena11">
eṉa maṉṉāṉaṉṟi ōcaivēṟupāṭṭāṉ orukāṟṟiṭpamiṉṟeṉṉun toṭakkattu oḻiyicaipporuṭōṉṟalum peṟappaṭum. poruṭkum poruḷaip pulaṉākavuṭaiya uṇarviṟkum oṟṟumai karutip poruḷuṇarvaip poruḷeṉṟār. “mikuti ceyyum poruḷ” eṉpatu mutalāyiṉavaṟṟiṟkum ītokkum.
          </p>
      <p xml:id="TolC250-Cena12">
okkumeṉṉuñcollaṉṟē oppumaiyuṇarttuvatu; accol āṇṭiṉmaiyāṉ oppumai tōṉṟāmaiyāṉ; oppilvaḻiyāleṉṟār; uvamaiyoṭu poruṭku oppillaiyeṉṟārallareṉpatu. okkumeṉṉuñcollai oppeṉṟāreṉpārumuḷar. oppilvaḻiyāṟporuḷ ceykunavāvaṉa, aṉṉa, ēyppa, uṟaḻa, oppa, eṉpaṉa mutalākap poruḷatikārattuk kūṟappaṭṭa muppattāṟaṉuḷ okkumeṉpatoḻiya ēṉaiyavām.
          </p>
      <p xml:id="TolC250-Cena13">
cāriyaiyum, vēṟṟumaiyurupum, uvamavurupum, kuṟippāṟporuḷuṇarttumāyiṉum, puṇarccikkaṇ upakārappaṭitalum vēṟṟumaittokaikkum uvamattokaikkum avavurupupaṟṟi ilakkaṇaṅkūṟutalum mutalākiya payaṉōkki, ivaṟṟai vēṟu kūṟiṉār.
          </p>
      <p xml:id="TolC250-Cena14">
iṭaiccolēḻaṉuḷḷum mutaṉiṉṟa mūṉṟum mēlēyuṇarttappaṭṭamaiyāṉ muṉ vaittār. oppilvaḻiyāṟ poruḷ ceykuna muṉṉaruṇarttappaṭutaliṉ iṟutikkaṇvaittār. oḻinta mūṉṟum ivvōttiṉkaṇ uṇarttappaṭutaliṉ iṭai vaittār.
          </p>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Nacciṉārkkiṉiyar</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Irāma. Kōvintacāmipiḷḷai</persName> 1997, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZM3kZpy.TVA_BOK_0008472/page/280/mode/1up">280</ref>–<ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZM3kZpy.TVA_BOK_0008472/page/282/mode/1up">282</ref>.</p>
      <p xml:id="TolC250-Nacc1">
iḵtu, avviṭaic coṟkaḷiṉ pākupāṭu kūṟu kiṉṟatu.
          </p>
      <p xml:id="TolC250-Nacc2">
(i-ḷ) avaitām-muṟkūṟiya iṭaic coṟkaṭām, puṇariya ṉilaiyiṭaip poruṇilaikkutanavum ― iru moḻi tammiṟ puṇartaliyaṉṟa nilaimaikka ṇavaṟṟiṉ poruṇilaik kutaviceytu varuvaṉavum, viṉaiceyal maruṅkiṟ kālamoṭu varunavum ― mutaṉilai niṉṟu kāriyattait tōṟṟuvikku miṭattuk kālaṅkāṭṭu miṭaic coṟkaḷōṭē pālu miṭamuṅkāṭṭu miṭaic coṟkaḷāy varuvaṉavum, vēṟṟumaip poruḷvayiṉuru pākunavum ― vēṟupāṭu ceyyuñ ceyappaṭuporuṇ mutalākiyavaṟṟiṉka ṇurupeṉṉuṅ kuṟiyavāy varuvaṉavum, acainilaik kiḷaviyāki varunavum ― tamakkōr poruḷiṉṟit tāñcārnta peyar viṉaikaḷaiyacaiyap paṇṇum nilaimaiyavāy varuvaṉavum, icainiṟaik kiḷaviyāki varunavum ― ceyyuṭka ṇicai niṟaittalē poruḷāka varuvaṉavum, tattaṅ kuṟippiṟ poruḷ ceykunavum ― kūṟuvār tāntāṅ kuṟitta kuṟippiṉālē yavarkaḷ kuṟitta poruḷai viḷakki niṟpaṉavum, oppil vaḻiyāl poruḷ ceykunavum-nāṭakavaḻakkiṉā ṉuyttuṇari ṉaṉṟi yulakiyal vaḻakkiṉāṟ kāṭṭappaṭuvatō roppiṉṟi niṉṟavoppumaip poruṇmaiyai yuṇarttivaru muvama urupukaḷum, eṉṟappaṇ piṉavē nuvaluṅ kālai-eṉṟu collappaṭṭa avvēḻiyal piṉaiyumuṭaiya collumiṭat teṉṟavāṟu.
          </p>
      <p xml:id="TolC250-Nacc3">
poruṇilaik kutavuvaṉa, vellā meṉpataṉai vaṟṟuc cāriyai yaḵṟiṇai yākkiyum, nammuc cāriyai yuyartiṇai yākkiyum, niṟpaṉa pōlvaṉa. itaṉāṉē, kāraṅ kara mutaliya veḻuttuc cāriyaiyuṅ koḷka.
          </p>
      <p xml:id="TolC250-Nacc4">
(u-m) uṇṭā ṉeṉpuḻi uṇṇeṉṉum mutaṉilai kālaṅkāṭṭukiṉṟa ṭakarattiṉaiyum, pālumiṭamuṅ kāṭṭum āṉiṉaiyum virittu niṉṟavāṟu kāṇka.
          </p>
      <p xml:id="TolC250-Nacc5">
uṇṭeṉṉu mecca mutaliyaṉavum pālu miṭamu muṇarttu meṉpatu, vantāṉ vantateṉṉum viṉaikaḷāṟ peṟutal.
        </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC250-Nacc5-q1">
            <l>‘piripuvēṟu paṭīiñ ceytiya vāki’<app><note xml:lang="en">Cf. <title xml:lang="ta">Tolkāppiyam Collatikāram Viṉaiyiyal</title> <ref target="https://projectmadurai.org/pm_etexts/utf8/pmuni0100.html#:~:text=%E0%AE%A4%E0%AE%BF%E0%AE%B0%E0%AE%BF%E0%AE%AA%E0%AF%81%20%E0%AE%B5%E0%AF%87%E0%AE%B1%E0%AF%81%E0%AE%AA%E0%AE%9F%E0%AF%82%E0%AE%89%E0%AE%AE%E0%AF%8D%20%E0%AE%9A%E0%AF%86%E0%AE%AF%E0%AF%8D%E0%AE%A4%E0%AE%BF%E0%AE%AF%20%E0%AE%86%E0%AE%95%E0%AE%BF">216</ref>.</note></app></l>
        </lg>
      <p xml:id="TolC250-Nacc6">
eṉpataṉāṟ koḷka.
        </p>
      <p xml:id="TolC250-Nacc7">
taṉṉiṉa muṭitta leṉpataṉāṉ, uṇṭava ṉeṉṟāṟ pōlun toḻiṟ peyarum, ‘nampi, naṅkai’ yeṉa varum peyarp peyarum ivviṭaiccoṟ peṟṟu varutal koḷka.
        </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC250-Nacc7-q1">
          <l>‘kaṇṇakaṉ ñālam’<app><note xml:lang="en">Cf. <title xml:lang="ta">Puṟanāṉūṟu</title> 35.</note></app></l>
        </lg>
      <p xml:id="TolC250-Nacc8">
eṉpuḻik kaṇ ṇiṭap poru ḷuṇarttutalu mūrttāleṉpuḻi kāluru pākalum muṟkūṟiṉām.
        </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC250-Nacc8-q1">
          <l>‘aṉaiyai yākaṉ māṟē’<app><note xml:lang="en">Cf. <title xml:lang="ta">Puṟanāṉūṟu</title> 4.</note></app> </l>
          <trailer>(puṟam)</trailer>
        </lg>
      <lg xml:id="TolC250-Nacc8-q2">
          <l>‘ciṟantōṉ peyaraṉ piṟanta māṟē’</l>
          <trailer>(<ref target="../Narrinai/NA40.xml?highlight=%5Bid%3D%22NA40%22%5D%20.l%3Anth-of-type(12)">naṟṟiṇai</ref>)</trailer>
        </lg>
      <p xml:id="TolC250-Nacc9">
eṉpuḻi māṟeṉṉu miṭaiccol viṉaiyai yaṭuttuk kāraṇap poruḷuṇartti niṟṟaliṉ, mūṉṟām vēṟṟumaip poruḷuṇartti niṉṟa tallāmai yuṇarka. atu, mūṉṟāvataṉ poruḷuṇarttiṟṟēl
        </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC250-Nacc9-q1">
          <l>‘kūṟāy tōḻiyām vāḻu māṟē’</l>
        </lg>
      <p xml:id="TolC250-Nacc10">
eṉpuḻi vāḻumāṟṟaiyeṉa viraṇṭālavatu viriyātām.
        </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC250-Nacc10-q1">
          <l>‘mantira vitiyiṉ’ marapuḷi vaḻā’</l>
          <trailer>(tirumuruku)</trailer>
        </lg>
      <p xml:id="TolC250-Nacc11">
eṉpuḻi, muraimaiyiṉ vaḻuvāta vantaṇareṉa vaintāvatu viritalāṉum.
        </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC250-Nacc11-q1">
          <l>‘iyalpuḷik kōlōccu maṉṉavaṉ’</l>
          <trailer>(<ref target="../Tirukkural/TK545.xml?highlight=%5Bid%3D%22TK545%22%5D%20.l%3Anth-of-type(1)">kuṟaḷ</ref>)</trailer>
        </lg>
      <p xml:id="TolC250-Nacc12">
eṉpuḻi, ‘muṟaimaiyilē ceṅkōṉaṭāttu meṉa vēḻaṉurupu viritalāṉum, uḷiyeṉpatu mūṉṟaṉurupiṉ poruṭpaṭa vantataṉṟu; pakutip poruḷ vikuti yāy niṉṟu taṉakkēṟṟa vurupaiyēṟṟu niṉṟatu. im mūṉṟum puṇariyaluḷḷum viṉaiyiyaluḷḷum vēṟṟumai yōttiṉuḷḷuṅ kūṟi yiṭai niṉṟa mūṉṟu mīṇṭuk kūṟukiṉṟār. iṟuti niṉṟa voppil vaḻiyāṟ poruḷ ceyyu muvamavurupukaḷ ‘aṉṉa vēyppa’ veṉṉuñ cūttirattā ṉuvamaviyaluṭ kūṟupa. avai yoppiṉṟi yoppuṇarttutal,
        </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC250-Nacc12-q1">
          <l>‘oppu muruvam veṟuppu meṉṟā’<app><note xml:lang="en">Cf. <title xml:lang="ta">Tolkāppiyam Poruḷatikāram Poruḷiyal</title> <ref target="https://projectmadurai.org/pm_etexts/utf8/pmuni0100.html#:~:text=%E0%AE%92%E0%AE%AA%E0%AF%8D%E0%AE%AA%E0%AF%81%E0%AE%AE%E0%AF%8D%20%E0%AE%89%E0%AE%B0%E0%AF%81%E0%AE%B5%E0%AF%81%E0%AE%AE%E0%AF%8D%20%E0%AE%B5%E0%AF%86%E0%AE%B1%E0%AF%81%E0%AE%AA%E0%AF%8D%E0%AE%AA%E0%AF%81%E0%AE%AE%E0%AF%8D%20%E0%AE%8E%E0%AE%A9%E0%AF%8D%E0%AE%B1%E0%AE%BE">51</ref>.</note></app></l>
        </lg>
      <p xml:id="TolC250-Nacc13">
veṉṉum poruḷiyaṟ cūttirattā ṉuṇarka.
        </p>
