  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Teyvaccilaiyār</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">1929, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZU1k0My.TVA_BOK_0007188/page/n172/mode/1up">165</ref>–<ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZU1k0My.TVA_BOK_0007188/page/n173/mode/1up">166</ref>.</p>
      <p xml:id="TolC250-Tey1">
iṭaiccōl pākupaṭūmāṟu uṇarttutal nutaliṟṟu.
          </p>
      <p xml:id="TolC250-Tey2">
i-ḷ: “avaitām puṇariyal nilaiyiṭaip poruḷ nilaikkutakavum” eṉpatu mēṟ collappaṭṭa iṭaiccoṟkaṭām oru col puṇarntiyalumvaḻi, apporuḷnilaikkutavi yāki varuvaṉavum eṉṟavāṟu. poruḷnilaikku utavalāvatu alvaḻip poruṭku uriyaṉa ivai, vēṟṟumaip poruṭku uriyaṉa ivaiyeṉa varutal. avaiyāvaṉa iṉṉē, aṟṟē eṉpaṉa mutalāyiṉa. avai cāriyai yaṉṟō eṉiṉ, avai iṭaiccol eṉavum oru kuṟi peṟum eṉṟavāṟu. ‘viṉai ceyal maruṅkiṟ kālamoṭu varukavum’ eṉṟatu viṉaiccol muṭivupeṟumiṭattuk kālaṅ kāṭṭuñ collōṭu pāl kāṭṭum collum eṉṟavāṟu. avaiyāvaṉa uṇṭaṉam, uṇṭām, uṇṇākiṉṟaṉam, uṇkiṉṟaṉam, uṇpam, uṇkuvam eṉpuḻi, iṟantakālaṅkuṟitta kuṟippōṭu, nikaḻkālaṅ kuṟitta niṉṟu, kiṉṟu eṉpaṉavum, etirkālaṅ kuṟitta pu, ku eṉpaṉavum, am ām eṉap pālkāṭṭuvaṉavum, ivvāṟu varuvaṉa piṟavum (ām.) ‘vēṟṟumaip poruḷvayiṉ urupākunavum’ eṉpatu avvēṟṟumaip poruḷiṭattu urupāki niṟkuñ coṟkaḷum eṉṟavāṟu. avaiyāvaṉa ai, oṭu, ku mutaliya. ivaiyum iṭaiccol eṉak kuṟipeṟṟaṉa. ‘acainilaikiḷaviyāki varunavum’ eṉpatu poruḷpaṭanillātu acainilai yāki niṟpaṉavum e-ṟu. ‘icainiṟaikkiḷavi yākivarunavum’ eṉpatu acainilaik kiḷavi pōlap pirintu nillātu, oru collōṭu oṟṟumaippaṭṭu icainiṟaittaṟ poruṭṭāki niṟpaṉavum ē-ṟu. ‘tattaṅ kuṟippiṟ poruḷcey kunavum’ eṉapatu tattaṅ kuṟippiṉāṟ poruḷ uṇarttuvaṉavum eṉṟavāṟu. ‘ōppil vaḻiyāṟ poruḷcey kunavum’ eṉpatu kuṟippiṉāl varu taliṉṟip poruttam illāta viṭattup poruḷ uṇarttuvaṉavum eṉṟavāṟu. ‘appaṇpiṉavē nuvaluṅkālai’ eṉpatu avviyalpiṉaiyuṭaiya: colluṅ kālattu. e-ṟu.
          </p>
      <p xml:id="TolC250-Tey3">
tattaṅ kuṟippiṉ eṉpataṟkuc cārnta colliṉ kuṟippiṉaṉ eṉavum, ōppilvaḻi eṉpataṉai oru collōṭu porutta miṉṟit taṉi vantuḻi eṉavum poruḷ uraippiṉum amaiyum. aḵtu aṟṟāka, oppilvaḻi eṉpataṟku okkum eṉṉuñ col vārāta uvama urupeṉap poruḷ uraippavāleṉiṉ, oppiṉāṉum paṇpiṉāṉumēṉ―ṟappāṟ kālaṅ kuṟippōṭu tōṉṟum eṉṟamaiyāṉum, pōla, aṉṉa ēyppa, uṟaḻa eṉpaṉa cāttaṉ ‘pulipōlum eṉavum, pulipōlap pāyntāṉ eṉavum, puli pōṉṟa cāttaṉ, pulipōluñ cāttaṉ eṉavum, ivvāṟu piṟavum, muṟṟum, viṉaiyeccamum, peyareccamumāki varutaliṉālum avai yellām viṉaikkuṟippeṉṟu koḷka. avaṟṟuḷ, ‘puṇariyal nilai yiṭaipporuḷ nilaikkutavuna’ eḻuttatikārattukkūṟappaṭṭaṉa. ‘vēṟṟumaip poruḷvayiṉ urupākuna’ vēṟṟumai yōttiṉuṭkūṟappaṭṭaṉa. ēṉai nāṉkum īṇṭu ōtappaṭukiṉṟaṉa. [2]
          </p>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Kallāṭaṉār</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Cuntaramūrtti</persName> 1964, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/TVG27Tolkappiyam/page/%E0%AF%A7%E0%AF%AF%E0%AF%AA/mode/1up">194</ref>–<ref target="https://archive.org/details/TVG27Tolkappiyam/page/%E0%AF%A7%E0%AF%AF%E0%AF%AB/mode/1up">195</ref>.</p>
      <p xml:id="TolC250-Kal1">
eṉ - eṉīṉ, avvieṭac coṟkaḷiṉ pākupāṭāmāṟu uṇarttutal nutaliṟṟu.
          </p>
      <p xml:id="TolC250-Kal2">
(i-ḷ.) mēl iṭaiccol eṉṟu collappaṭṭavai tām iru mōḻi tammiṟ puṇartaliyaṉṟa nilaimaikkaṇ avaṟṟiṉa poruṇilaimaikkutaviceytu varuvaṉavum, viṉaiccoṟkaḷai muṭikkumiṭattuk kālaṅkāṭṭum iṭaiccoṟkaḷoṭu kūṭit tām pālkāṭṭuñ coṟkaḷāy varuvaṉavum, vēṟupāṭu ceyta poruṇmaiyiṭattu vēṟṟumaiyurupāy varuvaṉavum, vaḻakkiṉkaṇ tamakku ōr poruḷiṉṟit tām aṭainta peyar viṉaikaḷai acaiyappaṇṇi niṟkum nilaimaiyavāy varuvaṉavum, peyarp poruḷiṭattup poruḷiṉṟi ōrōr acaiyai niṟaittaṟporuṇmaiyavāy varuvaṉavum, peyar viṉaikaḷpōla viḷaṅkap pōruḷuṇarttāta coṟkaḷ tattam kuṟippāvē oru poruḷai uṇarttivaruvaṉavum, otta eṉṉum vāypāṭutaṉkaṇ nillāta kūṟṟāṉē niṉṟa oppumaip poruṇmaiyai uṇartti varuvaṉavum eṉṟu collappaṭṭa avvilakkaṇaṅkalai uṭaiyaṉavām, avaṟṟaic colluṅkālattu, (e - ṟu.)
          </p>
      <p xml:id="TolC250-Kal3">
puṇarccikkaṇ varuvaṉa eḻuttōttiṉuḷ ‘iṉṉēvaṟṟē’ yeṉṉum cūttirattāṉ ōtappaṭṭaṉ.
          </p>
      <p xml:id="TolC250-Kal4">
iṉit taṉṉīṉamuṭittal eṉpataṉāṉ kāram, karam, kāṉ eṉṉum eḻuttuc cāriyaiyuṅ koḷḷappaṭum.
          </p>
      <p xml:id="TolC250-Kal5">
viṉaiccoṟkaḷ pālkāṭṭi varuvaṉa viṉaiyiyaluḷ, ‘am ām mutalāka’ īṟupaṟṟi ōtiṉavellām eṉak koḷka.
          </p>
      <p xml:id="TolC250-Kal6">
iṉi avviṉaic coṟkaḷ ‘kālamoṭu varunavum’ eṉṟataṉāl kālaṅkāṭṭi varuvaṉa uṇṭāṉ eṉpuḻi iṭaikkaṇ ṭakaramum, uṇṇāriṉṟāṉ eṉpuḻi āniṉṟum, uṇpāṉ eṉpuḻip pakaramum attaṉmaiya piṟavum eṉakkoḷka. kālam uṇartti varutalāṉ avai kālam eṉappaṭṭaṉa. uṇṭāṉ eṉpuḻik kālaṅkāṭṭum ṭakarattuṭaṉē pāl kāṭṭum āṉ vantavāṟu aṟika.
          </p>
      <p xml:id="TolC250-Kal7">
ivvāṟu pālum kālamum kāṭṭuvaṉa viṉaikkeṉṟōtiṉum ataṉaip perumpāṉmaiyākki uṇṭavaṉ eṉṟāṟpōlap peyākkuṅ koḷka.
          </p>
      <p xml:id="TolC250-Kal8">
iṉi oṉṟeṉa muṭittal eṉpataṉāl viṉaiccoṟkaṇ pāluṇarttuvaṉavēyaṉṟip peyarkkē uriya vāypāṭṭāl uṇarttuvaṉavuṅ koḷḷappaṭum. avai nampi, naṅkai eṉṉum ikara aikāra īṟupōlvaṉa eṉak koḷka.
          </p>
      <p xml:id="TolC250-Kal9">
vēṟṟumai yurupāy varuvaṉa vēṟṟumai yōttiṉuḷ ‘avaitām peyar ai ōṭu ku’ eṉṉum cūttirattup peyar oḻinta ēḻum eṉak koḷka. ivaṟṟai ōttu aṭaivupaṟṟi muṉ kūṟāttu, viṉaikkaṇ varuvaṉa perumpāṉmaiyākal paṟṟip pōlum.
          </p>
      <p xml:id="TolC250-Kal10">
maṟṟai acainilaiyum, icainiṟaiyum, kuṟippiṟ poruḷceykunavum ivvōttiṉuḷ tattam ciṟappuc cūttirattuḷḷē utāraṇaṅ kāṭṭappaṭum.
          </p>
      <p xml:id="TolC250-Kal11">
oppil vaḻiyāṟ poruḷ ceykunavaṟṟiṟku utāraṇam itaṉ piṉṉatikārattu uvamaiyiyaluḷ kāṇappaṭum.
          </p>
      <p xml:id="TolC250-Kal12">
iccūttirattu muṉṉaiya mūṉṟum muṉṉar ōtip pōntaṉavāka lāṉ muṉ vaikkappaṭṭaṉa. piṉṉaiyatu piṉṉatikārattuk kūṟalāl piṉ vaikkappaṭṭatu. iṭaiyaṉa ivvōttiṉuḷ cūṟappaṭutalāṉ iṭaikiṉṟaṉa.
          </p>
      <p xml:id="TolC250-Kal13">
āyiṉ iṭaikkaṇiṉṟa mūṉṟaṉuḷḷum poruḷ ceyvataṉai muṉ collātu acainilai icainiṟaikaḷai muṉ colliyatu eṉṉai eṉiṉ, ivai iraṇṭum oḻiya īṟṟiṉ muṉṉum piṉṉum niṉṟavaiyellām perumpāṉmaiyiṉavāy niṟṟalāṉum, avaitām ivaiyāy niṟṟalāṉum, ivaitām avaiyāyniṟṟal ciṟupāṉmaiyākalālum eṉpatu. (2)
          </p>
    </body>
